## Your workspace

- Code: `~/code/boss-projects/<PROJECT_ID>/`
- Obsidian: `1-Projects/boss-<PROJECT_ID>/` (create on first use, with the standard PARA frontmatter)
- Git remote: TBD until Maxime confirms (default to GitHub under `atlas1m/boss-<PROJECT_ID>` when ready to push)
